reviewText: Use this tape at our Senior Ministry.  They just love it.  Have also recommended it to other ministries.
Good workout.  Length of video great as it is easy to follow and encourages frequent use.
Enjoy the personality and enthusiasm.  The Exercises are what I wanted. Thanks
I enjoyed the exercise tape, kinda moves  at a faster pace than I'm use to but sure I will work my way up to Curtis' pace. I do get a good sweat going after only 1/2 hour with him.
clear and precise.  I like working out with it.
